WEBVTT

00:00:01.980 --> 00:00:05.305
(Music)

00:00:05.855 --> 00:00:10.610
Dannielle Hadley: Life
in Pennsylvania means just that:

00:00:10.610 --> 00:00:14.302
life without the possibility of parole.

00:00:14.302 --> 00:00:16.182
For us lifers,

00:00:16.182 --> 00:00:18.411
as we call ourselves,

00:00:18.411 --> 00:00:20.455
our only chance for release

00:00:20.455 --> 00:00:22.684
is through commutation,

00:00:22.684 --> 00:00:27.304
which has only been granted
to two women since 1989,

00:00:27.304 --> 00:00:30.105
close to 30 years ago.